com.coveros.selenified.services

Interface Check

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Assert, Verify

    public interface Check
    Check will handle all verifications performed on the actual web services calls themselves. These asserts are custom to the framework, and in addition to providing easy object oriented capabilities, they assist in troubleshooting and debugging failing tests.
    Version:
    3.2.0
    Author:
    Max Saperstone
